---
title: Country Chicken & Honey Butter Biscuits plus a side of Coleslaw
description: Craving some down-home-style comfort? We reckon you’ve come to the right place! We’re serving up chicken coated in a mix of panko, Monterey Jack, and bold blackening spices, flaky buttermilk biscuits slathered in honey butter, and a side of creamy coleslaw. The best part, though? Everything comes together in just 35 minutes! Dinner is served, ya’ll.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/country-chicken-honey-butter-biscuits-6eafcfa7.jpg
